<img src="images/music/watusi/watusi_cd.jpg" width="300px" />
<img src="images/music/watusi/watusi_promotional_insert.jpg" width="300px" /></p>

<p>The above scans are of my promotional copy of Watusi I received from Silage management company Straight Up Music.  It was autographed at my first Silage show.</p>

